## Component Documentation
* [[/docs/0.3/apps|Applications]]. How to map urls to python code paths.
    * [[/docs/0.3/apps/basic|Basic app]]. Map regexes to classes.
    * [[/docs/0.3/apps/auto|Auto app]]. Have webpy keep track of the urls based on class name.
    * [[/docs/0.3/apps/subdir|Subdir app]]. Host multiple apps based on the sub-directory.
    * [[/docs/0.3/apps/subdomain|Subdomain app]]. Host multiple apps based on the subdomain.
* [[/docs/0.3/templetor|Templates]]. Templetor, the web.py templating system
* [[/form|Forms]]. Dealing with user input
* [[/docs/0.3/app_processors|Application processors]]. Run code before each request.
* [[/docs/0.3/sessions|Sessions]]. Store persistent data per user across requests. 
* Database
* Testing

